  "description": {
    "zh": "看看谁来了，你好啊！我听到一些传言，说是在旧的军事基地仓库里还有很多食物。据传在军队离开后，强盗们开始在那里游荡。帮我个忙，找到他们的踪迹以及仓库所在的位置。你得注意安全，那里真的有很多混蛋游荡。",
    "en": "Look who we've got here! Hello there! Listen, you know about the military base close to the health resort? Probably were there yourself. So, I've got some news. They say the old warehouses there still have a lot of food left in them, and that bandit groups began roaming there, not your regular Scavs, they are well-equipped. I want you to check out if there's anything left in those warehouses. But be careful, there really are a lot of dangerous people there."
  },
